<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>대입 전략</title>
  <!-- CSV를 쉽게 읽는 도구(PapaParse)를 인터넷에서 불러옵니다 -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/papaparse@5.4.1/papaparse.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    body { font-family: "맑은 고딕", sans-serif; max-width: 880px;
           margin: 24px auto; padding: 0 16px; color: #222; }
    h1 { color: #1F3864; }
    .box { background:#F2F6FC; padding:16px; border-radius:8px; }
    input { font-size:18px; padding:6px 10px; width:120px; }
    button { font-size:18px; padding:7px 18px; background:#2E75B6;
             color:#fff; border:none; border-radius:6px; cursor:pointer; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width:100%; margin-top:16px; }
    th,td { border:1px solid #ccc; padding:6px 8px; font-size:14px; }
    th { background:#1F3864; color:#fff; }
    .safe{color:#1E7145;} .fit{color:#B58900;} .reach{color:#C00000;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>5등급제 -> 9등급 입결 기반 교과전형 찾기</h1>
  <div class="box">
    <label>내 5등급 평균 등급: </label>
    <input id="avg" type="number" step="0.01" min="1" max="3.5" value="1.50">
    <button onclick="run()">지원 가능 대학 찾기</button>
  </div>
  <div id="result">데이터를 불러오는 중입니다...</div>
 
  <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
